                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220522-118-off625 t18220522-118-cd626"></join>, nine yards of lace, value 30 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220522-118-victim1086" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Veall
